{"tid":426732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"弱智既女人做錯野之後係咪都會係咁？","createTime":"2017-10-07T01:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T05:16:14.000Z","uid":24615,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a3ae54ec2c60d90f9f0ec8bc85786a075f4c8f","tid":426732,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:44:05.000Z","msg":"首先做錯野累到人地/累到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n好驚好不知所措，但唔會諗到有效既解決方法，要由身邊既人/受害者去諗解決方法，冇人幫就周圍怨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n身邊既人指責/同佢講道理/向佢追究責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢就覺得人地傷口上灑鹽，我已經好驚好傍惶做咩仲要鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又喊又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事情得已解決後（由身邊既人幫手），就覺得自己好勇敢咁面對左個困難（冇諗過個麻煩係自己搞出黎，更加冇諗過比佢累到既受害人）做到個勇敢既女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己唔可以因爲呢d「不幸」（其實係佢自己搞出黎）而「從此害怕去愛」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，相信下次唔會有呢d不幸（完全冇反省過），結果下次發生時loop番去step1&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<br />\nLoop左好多次之後，開始覺得世界對自己好殘忍，開始自以爲「看破紅塵」去左下一個境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個亞歷山大老母又係，連續2次因爲開門唔幫隻狗綁狗帶 <br />\n搞到兩隻狗都比車車死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後就覺得自己好慘又剩，d弱智女人留言就話佢面對到好勇敢，仲要鼓勵佢叫佢唔好從此驚左養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有個連生三個白化症小朋友既老母又係，原來佢生完第一個就知自己同老公都有隱性基因，但都仲要繼續生（原因係「覺得」自已有能力照顧好） d留言都係讚佢好勇敢好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於個兩隻狗同三個小朋友點？wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9d44194165c4bf9418a100f30e7fa51fd2c7b3","tid":426732,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:14:01.000Z","msg":"完全同意"},{"pid":"511757e637c12372d8c5c8a757f034b91ba6ce58","tid":426732,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"鬼唔望車撚死個壓力山大"},{"pid":"c0e090f2dae1be5ea099ae67e67082adf5d78da2","tid":426732,"uid":84172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:25:47.000Z","msg":"個堆偽善留言至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等班弱智女真係以為自己好叻叻好有勇氣<br />\n累係累到佢周圍既人咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d118c3bc2f6dec9b75b3c38d13eda38b18cfda3","tid":426732,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個堆偽善留言至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等班弱智女真係以為自己好叻叻好有勇氣<br />\n累係累到佢周圍既人咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面有人留言叫佢下次養狗要照顧好d，唔好再比呢d事發生<br />\n<br />\n即刻好多人插佢話咩落井下石指責亞歷媽咩居心，仲叫亞歷媽唔好因為d人而怕左對狗狗既愛等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亞歷媽現在最需要的是大家關心和體諒，而不是落井下石的指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9c264f18f42b4503f88086f879e8cadcbdc531","tid":426732,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"通常做錯既不外乎感情事，做未婚媽媽，生左有問題小朋友，同埋寵物"},{"pid":"62e58c6ffbc0b21f70d462971086f60e4678aa32","tid":426732,"uid":15404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"聰明人，狡猾人，並不可怕。<br />\n最可怕是無知的人。<br />\n<br />\n見到呢d女人最想就係一巴巴車埋去"},{"pid":"691e65d57e6c6c09116601af608b9db6d4746d1a","tid":426732,"uid":57554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03